column13: There are disclosed novel 3-[(5-nitro-2-imidazolyl)pyrazol-5-yl]oxamic acid derivatives and salts thereof, exhibiting utility as antibacterial, antiprotozoal, and antifungal agents, making the compounds useful particularly in veterinary medicine, especially in controlling bacterial and protozoal infections of cattle, swine, and poultry.

column13: Novel bis(dihalonitromethyl)pyridines, useful as broad spectrum antimicrobials, are prepared from the corresponding nitronate salts, which have not previously been obtainable.
